Package snid

Interface Biometric

All Known Implementing Classes:
BiometricData
public interface Biometric
This defines the interactions the system should have with person's biometric data

    Gets the type of biometric data.
    java.lang.String getValue()

    Matches two biometric data sets.

  • Method Details

    • getTag

      java.lang.String getTag()
      Gets the type of biometric data. 'F' represents Fingerprint. 'D' represents DNA.
      Returns:
      a String representing the biometric type

    • getValue

      java.lang.String getValue()
      Gets the biometric value for the person
      Returns:
      A string representing the biometric value for that person

    • match

      int match​(Biometric other)
      Matches two biometric data sets.
      Parameters:
      other - another set of biometric data
      Returns:
      a number represent whether or not the match was successful
